data.description: Welcome to your future home sweet home! Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this charming residence is the epitome of comfort and style. The heart of the home, the spacious living room, invites you to unwind and create lasting memories with loved ones. In addition there is a large dining room, den, spacious kitchen and separate laundry. The primary bedroom features a huge en suite with a walk in closet the size of a bedroom! Step outside to discover your private oasis—an expansive backyard with a detached garage and built in office space. Just a stones throw to the casino, this could be the perfect Airbnb as well.  Recent updates include Roof & Water Heater (2013), Hvac (new duct work) & Windows (2016), freshly painted, floors refinished, new toilets, faucets, and electrical. Come see today!
